    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it! It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in truly pristine, showroom condition. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found. I'm looking for someone who will love and cherish it as much as I have. It's ready for its next adventure today!",
