    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presented in concours-level condition, this 2011 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.2) is a superlative example of the marque\u2019s last hydraulic-steering analog masterpiece. Powered by a 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six, it delivers 385 hp through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. Mechanical highlights include Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a mechanical locking rear differential, providing exceptional lateral grip and chassis composure. The vehicle exhibits zero bore scoring symptoms and has a clean DME report with no ignitions in high-rev ranges. Every bushing, seal, and fluid is up to date, ensuring the high-revving boxer engine performs with factory-spec compression and thermal efficiency. An unblemished, collector-grade specimen for the serious driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Mint condition. Garage kept. Single owner. No accidents. Full service history included.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute time capsule, maintained to the highest possible standards and presented in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster with zero rock chips or swirl marks, thanks to a professional ceramic coating and climate-controlled garage storage. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the dashboard remains free of any UV damage. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, this car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio with all maintenance performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. It has never seen rain, let alone winter conditions, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a turn-key example that requires absolutely nothing but a new home.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, currently held in impeccable, showroom-grade condition. This unit has been curated for the most discerning clientele, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Beyond its aesthetic perfection, the vehicle has undergone a comprehensive mechanical validation to ensure peak performance. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a masterfully preserved example that represents the pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 48500.0,
