    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home! This car is in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014it basically looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garaged, and stayed on top of every single service. It drives like an absolute dream! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been truly loved and cared for, this is the one. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take a peek! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
