      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the S65 4.0L V8 powerplant, utilizing individual throttle bodies to achieve a surgical 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. This vehicle is mechanically flawless, with documented preventive rod bearing and throttle actuator services. The Alpine White finish remains in showroom state, complemented by a pristine carbon fiber roof with no resin delamination. The interior reflects zero bolster wear on the Novillo leather, maintaining factory-spec tactile feedback. A turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the serious driver.",
